            <title>[LU-8979] Disable lock reprocessing at recovery</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8979</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre should disable &lt;tt&gt;ldlm_reprocess_all()&lt;/tt&gt; all the time when the target is in recovery, otherwise the locks in the waiting list may be &apos;wrongly&apos; granted if the conflicting granted locks are not replayed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
